<p>And then how to host our website/blog for free on specific platforms such as <a href="https://gitlab.com/terminalroot">Gitlab</a>, <a href="https://github.com/terroo">Github</a>, <a href="https://marcos.netlify.com/">Netlify</a> and others, as well as using your own domain for our address, how to easily create posts, Jekyll structure and several other tips.</p>

